      • convert

        public SchemaDocument convert​(ShapeIndex shapeIndex,
                              Shape shape)
        Perform the conversion of a single shape.

        The root shape of the created document is set to the given shape, and only shapes connected to the given shape are added as a definition.

        shapeIndex - Shape index to convert.
